Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:33.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:36.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers who\Nkeep a close eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:42.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the countless souls, good and evil,\Nthat fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen, who has brought chaos\Nupon the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to set his plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:53.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancars, created by Aizen\Nusing the Hogyoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a material that removes the boundaries\Nbetween Soul Reapers and Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time, Visored,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers who have awakened\Nthe powers of the Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear before Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:13.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako, one of the Visored,\Ninvites Ichigo to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensing the power of the Hollow\Ndwelling within,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo feels fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:26.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he challenges the Arrancars,\NUlquiorra and Yammy, sent by Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do, Ulquiorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a rare power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we take her alive\Nand present her to Aizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:38.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:45.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not necessary.\NErase her, Yammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...for being late, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm sorry, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If only I was stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize, Inoue.\NAnd don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:36.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tensa Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...\NThis is Kurosaki's Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\NI'm seeing it up close,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:08.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels a bit different from\Nwhat I felt on Sokyoku Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure is\Nviolent and rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so heavy and thick,\NI can barely breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:24.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this isn't Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue. Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ulquiorra...\NThis guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Who would have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:52.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,your silly maneuvers would\Nsmoke him out so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange hair...\NA black Bankai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.\NHe's our target, Yammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved us the trouble\Nof searching, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suerte!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who hurt\NChad's right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! So what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- My arm! My arm!\N- You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn! What's this?!\N- That's what you get for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's this?!\N- lunging out like that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,without gauging the enemy's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I keep telling you\Nto master the Pesquisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He sliced through\NYammy's Hierro, Iron Skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and cut off his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's only been a short while\Nsince he learned to use Bankai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But his Spiritual Pressure\Nis exceedingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:58.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this level of power can't possibly\Npose a threat to Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tough, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:12.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're having a hard time.\NShall I take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to resort to\Nyour zanpakuto for a foe like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that sword at his waist\Nis a zanpakuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The cracked Hollow mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole in his chest... Zanpakuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was heading over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Spiritual Pressure\Nfelt odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they like us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Hirako and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you switch with me,\NI'll take care this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear! Disappear!\NDisappear! Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:40.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I deny you...\Nso now you'll get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he suddenly stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's Spiritual Pressure\Nresonance has suddenly increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the range of his resonance\Nis abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's low,\Nhis Pressure is trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it's high,\Nit's more than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Break apart and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late! Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,People keep getting in the way.\NIt's such a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:53.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming between us means\Nyou're asking to be killed first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tend to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How...is...Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:09:59.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you swallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a graceful loser, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll teach you!\NI pulverized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can dodge\Nmy Sero from this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! Whaddya do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you live through my Sero...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I deflected it, I would have put\Nthe others in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:49.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just used something similar\Nto offset it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't believe me,\Nshall I demonstrate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream... Benihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulquiorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! The blood's gone\Nto your head, Yammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are Kisuke Urahara\Nand Yoruichi Shihoin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:29.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At your level,\Nyou don't stand a chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A very foolish taunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you would fight me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:46.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,while trying to protect trash who\Nare on the verge of death...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, you know the odds lie\Nin my favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, our mission is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll report to Lord Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:01.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the wannabe Soul Reaper\Nhe has set his eyes on...is trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ururu, Jinta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Yoruichi's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your arm is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My arms and legs are fine\Nfor everyday living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And in combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up by not striking\Na blow while using Shunko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that\Nthe Arrancar's outer skin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,would be so dense\Nin Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke... They're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, they're much stronger\Nthan what we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying, annoying,\Nannoying, annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:52.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so depressing in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On a day like this, it's best to go out\Nand pick up some gals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Damn, freeloaders have\Nto be so considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:21.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! I'm risking my body like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Show some reaction at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm gonna find a cute gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't introduce you to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have some fun all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:41.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of fun!\NToo bad if you regret it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me, you punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ichigo...\Nwhat's wrong with him anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's causing a disturbance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- outside the house!\N- Oh no! Th-That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's Bostov!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:10.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!\NOh, you're so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be down in the dumps like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Orihime?!\NYou're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:10.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I fell down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have fallen down\Nthe stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:22.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were absent for five days!\NAnd look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to hug me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chizuru.\NI need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I jumped in without anybody\Nasking and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I got hurt without anybody asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So...please don't look like that\Nand don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Chad was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki nearly died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what\NI can do other than apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:13.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when we were leaving,\Nyou had that note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon Renji, you show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know your way around\Nthe World of the Living, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit rambling on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just search for the Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But World of the Living guys\Nwear such weird clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Students on this side are\Nrequired to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you studied up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, something's wrong with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, these clothes are so tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then be like us and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,don't tuck your shirt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:54.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! If I did that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to push\Nmy sword through my belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think the sword\Nis wrong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You guys said\NI couldn't bring a real sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm making do with\Na wooden one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:08.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the law in\Nthe World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of law says\Na real sword is bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sorta like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one pleased\Nwith your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to cause\Na disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then start by walking quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are. It's this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:31.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! How you doing, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Renji?! Ikkaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika, Rangiku...Toshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Captain Hitsugaya to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What...are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were ordered to enter this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to prepare for a full-on battle\Nwith the Arrancars,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and join up with\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arran...? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:16.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Were you fighting without\Nknowing who your opponents were?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:25.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those guys who beat you up\Nthe other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, what's with that get-up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:24.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NEverybody likes uniforms, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:27.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also come up with\Na nurse's outfit and a maid's outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:29.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, umm... A maid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about dressing up\Nour captain as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he seemed against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:36.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:38.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:43.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:46.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't see any meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:46.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:48.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:54.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?\NIt's okay, I prepared some.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, where'd you get it?\NThis meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:02.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it by the front door earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Bonnie!